### Configuração de variáveis

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@contentType = application/json
@authToken = Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

### ==========================================

### PROCEDURES DE VÍDEOS

### ==========================================

### 1. Criar novo vídeo

POST {{baseUrl}}/rpc/videos.createVideo
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
    "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ",
    "title": "Never Gonna Give You Up",
    "thumbnail": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/dQw4w9WgXcQ/hqdefault.jpg",
    "platform": "youtube",
    "videoId": "dQw4w9WgXcQ",
    "tagNames": ["music", "classic"],
    "isFavorite": false
}

###

### 2. Atualizar estado do vídeo

POST {{baseUrl}}/rpc/videos.updateVideo
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
    "videoId": "VIDEO_ID_AQUI",
    "isFavorite": true,
    "isWatched": false
}

###

### 3. Apagar vídeo

POST {{baseUrl}}/rpc/videos.deleteVideo
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
    "videoId": "VIDEO_ID_AQUI"
}

###

### 4. Adicionar tags ao vídeo

POST {{baseUrl}}/rpc/videos.addTagsToVideo
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
    "videoId": "VIDEO_ID_AQUI",
    "tagNames": ["tutorial", "tech"]
}

###

### 5. Remover tags do vídeo

POST {{baseUrl}}/rpc/videos.removeTagsFromVideo
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
    "videoId": "VIDEO_ID_AQUI",
    "tagIds": ["TAG_ID_1", "TAG_ID_2"]
}

###

### 6. Obter vídeos do utilizador

GET {{baseUrl}}/rpc/videos.getUserVideos
Authorization: {{authToken}}

